								<div itemprop="articleBody">
		<p><strong>GADDIEL </strong>team has experience in providing services and solutions on Product Development – both mobile and web applications, Custom Application to suite specific client needs, designing and developing website and web solutions, providing enhancement, maintenance and support services for existing live applications.  We have expertise across the entire Software Development Lifecycle, be it a product or custom application.</p>
<p><strong>GADDIEL </strong>team’s philosophy is customer centric with commitment to fulfill the client needs within the boundaries of the contracted engagement.  We work closely with our clients to realize their goals and always maintain a professional and result driven approach.</p>
<p><strong>GADDIEL </strong>team believes in continuing relationship with the customer and support them to achieve the best Returns On Investment.  We provide a flexible support service after the implementation phase of any business solution at any level, be it a full scale implementation or a simple customized solution.</p>
<p><strong>GADDIEL </strong> team knows that people are its greatest asset.  To meet the complex requirement of providing IT Solution, Support and Services, the team require the skills and efforts of a diverse group of people, engaged in a wide variety of activities.  Gaddiel team is fully equipped to meet the requirements by training, self-learning and implementation.  The team has a free hand in learning and adopting new technologies.</p> 	</div>

	
